## ğŸ“‚ Understanding the Linux File System

In Linux, everything is a file.

Important directories:

```
/home     â†’ user files
/etc      â†’ system configuration
/var/log  â†’ log files
/tmp      â†’ temporary files
/root     â†’ admin directory
/bin      â†’ essential commands
```

Understanding this structure = understanding the system.

